OL,3,CBereavement cafe believes people need
OL,4,Cbetter support to 'manage our grief'
OL,6,FThe new Cumbrian bereavement cafe
OL,7,Fbelieves people need better support to
OL,8,F"manage our grief" as demand for their
OL,9,Fservice is higher than ever.
OL,11,FA Comfort Cafe, in Cockermouth,
OL,12,Fprovides a space for people who are
OL,13,Fdealing with the death of their loved
OL,14,Fones.
OL,16,FThe Linking Lives charity and the
OL,17,Ftown's Churches Together group started
OL,18,Fthe initiative with the aim to provide
OL,19,Fan informal setting for people to
OL,20,Fsocialise.
