OL,3,CBereavement cafe believes people need
OL,4,Cbetter support to 'manage our grief'
OL,6,FLorraine Durham says she lost her son
OL,7,Fand brother within a few years of each
OL,8,Fother. She said: "My first experience
OL,9,Fof grief, I was 16, but I didn't know
OL,10,Fanything about it. And then when I was
OL,11,F19 - my two best friends.
OL,13,F"But the one that really hit me was my
OL,14,Fbrother, which was just over four
OL,15,Fyears ago. And then after that, two
OL,16,Fyears and two months after my brother
OL,17,Fpassed away, my son passed away
OL,18,Fsuddenly.
