OL,6,FThe two-year project began by
OL,7,Fdelivering training in bereavement
OL,8,Fsupport skills, expanding into
OL,9,Fdifferent areas including such as
OL,10,Fthose who have lost ones to suicide,
OL,11,Fand caring for children who are
OL,12,Fgrieving.
