OL,3,CBereavement cafe believes people need
OL,4,Cbetter support to 'manage our grief'
OL,6,FBill said: "We talk about all sorts of
OL,7,Fthings and we have a laugh. I think
OL,8,Fsome people at first tend to avoid you
OL,9,Fbecause they don't know what to say,
OL,10,Fyou know, and they maybe feel awkward
OL,11,Fabout it."
OL,13,FThe Comfort Cafe sessions will take
OL,14,Fplace fortnightly at Christ Church's
OL,15,Fcommunity hall in South Street, on the
OL,16,Fsecond and fourth Thursdays of the
OL,17,Fmonth, from 10.30am to 12.30pm.
